sem <- df_factors %>% 
  filter(Task == "Syntactic") %>% 
  mutate(
         Syntactic = ifelse(grepl("verb", Category), "verb", 
                    ifelse(grepl("noun", Category), "noun", NA)),
         Valence =  ifelse(grepl("positive", ConcValCombo), "positive", 
                    ifelse(grepl("negative", ConcValCombo), "negative", NA)),
        cConcValCombo = as.numeric(ConcValCombo) - mean(as.numeric(ConcValCombo)),
        cCategory = as.numeric(Category) - mean(as.numeric(Category)),
        # cSyntactic = as.numeric(factor(Syntactic)) - mean(as.numeric(factor(Syntactic)))
  )
